## Styles/Core: kColors.sys

## Transparent
ColorSet 15 RootTransparent Buffer, Tint #4a516a 60, fg white, bg black

## No borderline
Colorset 19 fg #ffffff, bg #2b4e5e, hi #2b4e5e, sh #2b4e5e
Colorset 191 fg #ffffff, bg #4e3715, hi #2b4e5e, sh #2b4e5e

